item.title: Helper Gets Admin on 317
item.dc:creator: @xnightmarepkz_rocks xnightmarepkz rocks
item.description:
@xnightmarepkz_rocks wrote:

Get Bittorent here. http://www.bittorrent.com Then Download it. when its done downloading, Open it. Go to
Options > Preferences > Type 43594 in your port. apply, and click okay. Then keep it up, along with DUC, And your server should be open to the public. Also Out of the blue, try ‘Runserver’ You need that to Run your server…

Tah-Dah.
